Interface IModelContainer

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IAssemblyClassBinding, IAssemblyDefinition, IBoundAssemblyDefinition, IChoiceInstance, IXmlAssemblyDefinition, IXmlChoiceInstance, IXmlModelContainer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractChoiceInstance, DefaultAssemblyClassBinding, XmlChoiceInstance, XmlGlobalAssemblyDefinition, XmlLocalAssemblyDefinition.InternalAssemblyDefinition
    public interface IModelContainer
    Indicates that the Metaschema definition type has a complex model that can contain flags, field, and assembly instances.
